                    [name] => Large Party Room Upgrade - 70% OFF
                    [index] => 1
                    [description] => <p data-start="186" data-end="411">Take your celebration to the next level with our spacious <strong data-start="244" data-end="264">Large Party Room</strong>&nbsp;for the entire duration of your Birthday Party Package &mdash; the perfect upgrade from the shared lobby area. Enjoy your own private space equipped with everything you need to host an unforgettable event:</p>
