    [name] => 3 HOUR FACILITY RENTAL (up to 120 guests)
    [description] => <div class="OutlineElement Ltr  BCX0 SCXO146644695">
<p class="Paragraph SCXO146644695 BCX0" lang="EN-US" xml:lang="EN-US"><span class="TextRun SCXO146644695 BCX0" lang="EN-US" xml:lang="EN-US" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXO146644695 BCX0">A Facility Rental at Flee Escape Rooms and Zero Latency VR</span><span class="NormalTextRun SCXO146644695 BCX0">&nbsp;is our best option for large parties and team outings. Made with the&nbsp;</span></span><span class="TextRun SCXO146644695 BCX0" lang="EN-US" xml:lang="EN-US" data-contrast="auto">customizability in mind, a Facility Rental allows access to all of our escape rooms and VR experiences.&nbsp;</span><span class="EOP SCXO146644695 BCX0">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p class="Paragraph SCXO146644695 BCX0" lang="EN-US" xml:lang="EN-US"><span style="font-size: small;"><span class="EOP SCXO146644695 BCX0">&nbsp;</span></span></p>
<p class="Paragraph SCXO146644695 BCX0" lang="EN-US" xml:lang="EN-US"><span style="font-size: small;"><span class="EOP SCXO146644695 BCX0"><span class="TextRun SCXO146644695 BCX0" lang="EN-US" xml:lang="EN-US" data-contrast="auto">Each Facility Rental must go through an approval process to ensure our team is able to accommodate your event. Your deposit will be refunded within 48 hours if we cannot accommodate your booking request for any reason.</span></span></span></p>
</div>
<div class="OutlineElement Ltr  BCX0 SCXO146644695">
<p class="Paragraph SCXO146644695 BCX0" lang="EN-US" xml:lang="EN-US"><span class="EOP SCXO146644695 BCX0" style="font-size: small;">&nbsp;</span></p>
</div>
<div class="OutlineElement Ltr  BCX0 SCXO146644695">
<p class="Paragraph SCXO146644695 BCX0" lang="EN-US" xml:lang="EN-US"><span style="font-size: small;"><span class="TextRun SCXO146644695 BCX0" lang="EN-US" xml:lang="EN-US" data-contrast="auto">The Facility Rental comes standard with access to the all escape rooms, free roam VR Arena, arcades &amp; lobby games; 12' table for catering/food, 2 party rooms and plenty of space in the lobby for seating.&nbsp;</span><span class="TextRun SCXO146644695 BCX0" lang="EN-US" xml:lang="EN-US" data-contrast="auto">Our escape games &amp; VR arena allow a max of 60 players in the same hour. Capacity is 200. Larger groups will be able to rotate among different experiences ensuring every guest is active during your event.</span><span class="EOP SCXO146644695 BCX0">&nbsp;</span></span></p>
</div>
<div class="OutlineElement Ltr  BCX0 SCXO146644695">
<p class="Paragraph SCXO146644695 BCX0" lang="EN-US" xml:lang="EN-US"><span class="EOP SCXO146644695 BCX0" style="font-size: small;">&nbsp;</span></p>
</div>
<div class="OutlineElement Ltr  BCX0 SCXO146644695">
<p class="Paragraph SCXO146644695 BCX0" lang="EN-US" xml:lang="EN-US"><span class="TextRun SCXO146644695 BCX0" style="font-size: small;" lang="EN-US" xml:lang="EN-US" data-contrast="auto">You are welcome to order catering or delivery, or bring any food/drinks you'll require for your event.</span></p>
</div>
<div class="OutlineElement Ltr  BCX0 SCXO146644695">
<p class="Paragraph SCXO146644695 BCX0" lang="EN-US" xml:lang="EN-US"><span class="EOP SCXO146644695 BCX0" style="font-size: small;">&nbsp;</span></p>
</div>
<div class="OutlineElement Ltr  BCX0 SCXO146644695">
<p class="Paragraph SCXO146644695 BCX0" lang="EN-US" xml:lang="EN-US"><span style="font-size: small;"><span class="TextRun SCXO146644695 BCX0" lang="EN-US" xml:lang="EN-US" data-contrast="auto">If you have any further questions or special requests for your event, please reach out to us! Email:&nbsp;</span><a href="mailto:info@fleeescape.com" rel="noreferrer noopener" target="_blank"><span class="TextRun SCXO146644695 BCX0" lang="EN-US" xml:lang="EN-US" data-contrast="auto">info@fleeescape.com</span></a><span class="TextRun SCXO146644695 BCX0" lang="EN-US" xml:lang="EN-US" data-contrast="auto">&nbsp;Phone: (425)287-1426</span></span></p>
</div>
