<p dir="ltr"><span style="color: #c0c0c0; font-size: medium;">It&rsquo;s the roaring 20s and you&rsquo;ve been invited to an exclusive party at the fanciest hotel around. You&rsquo;ve always wanted to try one of those newfangled lifts but just as you begin your ascent you hear a crash! Suddenly, you&rsquo;re no longer moving. It&rsquo;s up to you to repair this broken lift within 60 minutes or else you&rsquo;ll be late to your party!</span></p>
<p dir="ltr"><span style="font-size: medium;">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p dir="ltr"><span style="color: #c0c0c0; font-size: medium;">The Lift is our only single-room experience, and it&rsquo;s still packed full of brainteasers. Put your inner mechanic to the test to solve the hands-on puzzles inside! We also consider this room as one of the best rooms for beginners. A swingin&rsquo; good time!</span></p>
