Array
(
    [name] => ESCAPE GAME + VR PARTY PACKAGE (Up to 8 players; 1.5 Hour Game + 1 Hour Party) Age 9 or above and at least 4'5" tall
    [description] => <p><strong>(<span class="TextRun SCXO146644695 BCX0" lang="EN-US" xml:lang="EN-US" data-contrast="auto">Each Facility Rental must go through an approval process to ensure our team is able to accommodate your event. Your payment will be refunded within 48 hours if we cannot confirm your booking.)</span></strong></p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p>Host a very special day with Flee Escape Rooms and Zero Latency VR Seattle!</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p><span>This is what our exciting Escape Room and Zero Latency VR 2.5 Hour Party Package involves:</span></p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<ol>
<li><span>1 Hour of Escape Rooms for 8 players. You will get 1 escape rooms of your choice (or whichever is available) with 8 players in the room.&nbsp;</span></li>
<li><span>Once the Escape Rooms are done, your group will then move to 30 minutes of free roaming VR game from Zero Latency VR. VR game session is 30 minutes long and can have a maximum of 8 players in the session. As part of this package, you will get 1 30 min VR game sessions for any game of your choice. There will be $50 extra charge if you want to upgrade to our newest addition - 45 minutes of Space Marine VR Threat Lethal Extra game instead.</span></li>
<li><span>1 Hour of Party time in our open lobby area that includes a 14' party table with a decoration table cloth and 16 chairs. Note: If there is no prior party prior to your party package, we will give away the open lobby area for the entire duration of your event at no extra charge.</span></li>
</ol>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p>You can bring any refreshments (cake, food, or drink), or decorations you require. If you need refrigeration for any of the items, we highly recommend upgrading to our private large party room instead that has a refrigerator, microwave, TV, Xbox, and a kitchenette and fits 35+ people. Large party room is $125/hr but available at a 50% discount as part of this package.</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p>We recommend all players to at least Age 9 or above and at least 4'5" tall to be able to handle the VR headset and game controller.&nbsp;</p>
