    [name] => MUSEUM HEIST (PRIVATE GAME ONLY)
    [description] => <p dir="ltr"><span style="font-family: 'arial black', 'avant garde'; font-size: large; color: #c0c0c0;">Players: 2-8&nbsp;</span></p>
<p dir="ltr"><span style="font-family: 'arial black', 'avant garde'; font-size: large; color: #c0c0c0;">Difficulty: Advanced</span></p>
<p dir="ltr"><span style="font-family: 'arial black', 'avant garde'; font-size: large; color: #c0c0c0;">Success Rate: 35%</span></p>
<p dir="ltr"><span style="font-family: 'arial black', 'avant garde'; font-size: large; color: #c0c0c0;">Price: $40/Player ($45/player for a group of 2)</span></p>
<p dir="ltr"><span style="color: #c0c0c0;">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p dir="ltr"><span style="font-size: medium; color: #c0c0c0;">You and your team are master thieves who&rsquo;ve just broken into the private gallery of your rival: the art collector Dr. Voxman.</span></p>
<p dir="ltr"><span style="font-size: medium; color: #c0c0c0;">Dr. Voxman has been boasting that he&rsquo;ll reveal his collection&rsquo;s newest and most valuable piece of artwork at an auction, which is to be held tomorrow morning. Before that auction, he has hidden this mysterious piece in his intricately designed personal museum!</span></p>
<p dir="ltr"><span style="font-size: medium; color: #c0c0c0;">You don&rsquo;t know precisely what you&rsquo;re trying to steal, or where Dr. Voxman has hidden it, but you do know that it&rsquo;ll fetch a high price on the black market. The security systems will be re-enabled in 60 minutes&hellip; will you work quickly enough to steal the art before time runs out?&nbsp;</span></p>
<p dir="ltr"><span style="font-size: medium; color: #c0c0c0;">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p dir="ltr"><span style="font-size: medium; color: #c0c0c0;">Museum Heist is a multi-room experience that has many intricate puzzles and locks to open. It requires a high level of teamwork to succeed. It definitely puts the &ldquo;grand&rdquo; in grand larceny. This is our most difficult room, so come prepared for a challenge!</span></p>
