    [description] => <p><strong><span class="TextRun SCXO146644695 BCX0" lang="EN-US" xml:lang="EN-US" data-contrast="auto">(Party Package booking must go through an approval process to ensure our team is able to accommodate your event. You can request the escape room of your choice that you would want to reserve as part of this package however we cannot guarantee those rooms will be available based on the time slot. If those escape rooms are not available, we will book the other ones that might be available)</span></strong></p>
