                    [description] => <p>Please provide your selection of escape rooms (minimum of 2 escape rooms) for your booking request. You can list the escape rooms from&nbsp;<strong>most preferred to least preferred</strong>&nbsp;and our staff will do their best to accommodate your request based on the availability of the escape rooms.&nbsp;</p>
