<p dir="ltr"><span style="color: #c0c0c0;">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p dir="ltr"><span style="font-size: medium; color: #c0c0c0;">You are a team of archeologists who have been invited to join Professor Stanley Croft&rsquo;s Egyptian expedition. However, once you arrived, you discovered that the Professor has been missing for a few days now. You then decided to delve into one of the deeper, unexplored tombs in search of him, but as you entered the stone door collapsed behind you! You know there&rsquo;s a sandstorm arriving in 60 minutes, and if you can&rsquo;t find another way out, you just may become a part of history...</span></p>
<p dir="ltr"><span style="font-size: medium; color: #c0c0c0;">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p dir="ltr"><span style="font-size: medium; color: #c0c0c0;">Ancient Egypt is a multi-room experience that challenges players with a mix of cerebral and physical puzzles. Put your pyraMINDS to the test. This room&rsquo;s floor is entirely covered in sand, so be sure to wear appropriate shoes!</span></p>
