<p><br />You can bring any refreshments (cake, food, or drink), or decorations you require. If you need refrigeration for any of the items, we highly recommend upgrading to our private large party room instead that has a refrigerator, microwave, TV, Xbox, and a kitchenette and fits 35+ people. Large party room is $125/hr but available at a 50% discount as part of this package.</p>
