<p dir="ltr"><span style="font-size: medium; color: #c0c0c0;">You are a group of brave warriors who have been given your most important task yet: to save the realm from eternal winter! You must sneak into the Ice King&rsquo;s castle and disrupt his ritual before it is complete, or else the kingdom may never feel the touch of the sun again. You have 60 minutes before the ritual is complete. You must hurry!</span></p>
<p dir="ltr"><span style="color: #c0c0c0;">&nbsp;</span></p>
