    [name] => SMALL PRIVATE PARTY ROOM (50 mins rental) - Accommodates up to 15 People 
    [description] => <p><span style="font-size: medium;"><strong>Our small private party room is ~100 sf with maximum capacity of 15. (Equipped 80&ldquo; flat TV, speakers &amp; microphone, and a microwave)&nbsp;</strong></span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: medium;">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: medium;">The party room is great space for eating cake and opening presents after going through any of our escape rooms, free-roam VR games. Your party will have the room for hour aft your escape room. Catering is welcome!</span></p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p><span style="font-size: medium;">Note: If you need a refrigerator for your drinks and cake, we recommend booking our large party room instead.</span></p>
