    [name] => 2 HOUR FACILITY RENTAL (up to 40 guests)
    [description] => <div class="OutlineElement Ltr  BCX0 SCXO146644695">
<p class="Paragraph SCXO146644695 BCX0" lang="EN-US" xml:lang="EN-US"><span style="font-size: large;"><span class="TextRun SCXO146644695 BCX0" lang="EN-US" xml:lang="EN-US" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXO146644695 BCX0">A Facility Rental at Flee Escape Rooms and Zero Latency VR</span><span class="NormalTextRun SCXO146644695 BCX0">&nbsp;is our best option for large parties and team outings. Made with the&nbsp;</span></span><span class="TextRun SCXO146644695 BCX0" lang="EN-US" xml:lang="EN-US" data-contrast="auto">customizability in mind, a Facility Rental allows access to all of our experiences.&nbsp;</span><span class="EOP SCXO146644695 BCX0">&nbsp;</span></span></p>
</div>
<div class="OutlineElement Ltr  BCX0 SCXO146644695">
<p class="Paragraph SCXO146644695 BCX0" lang="EN-US" xml:lang="EN-US"><span class="EOP SCXO146644695 BCX0" style="font-size: large;">&nbsp;</span></p>
</div>
<div class="OutlineElement Ltr  BCX0 SCXO146644695">
<p class="Paragraph SCXO146644695 BCX0" lang="EN-US" xml:lang="EN-US"><span style="font-size: large;"><span class="TextRun SCXO146644695 BCX0" lang="EN-US" xml:lang="EN-US" data-contrast="auto">The Facility Rental comes standard with access to the all escape rooms, free roam VR Arena, arcade &amp; lobby games, 12' table for catering/food, 2 party rooms and plenty of space in the lobby for seating.&nbsp;</span><span class="TextRun SCXO146644695 BCX0" lang="EN-US" xml:lang="EN-US" data-contrast="auto">Our escape games &amp; VR arena allow a max of 60 players in the same hour. Capacity is 300. Larger groups will be able to rotate among different experiences ensuring every guest is active during your event.</span><span class="EOP SCXO146644695 BCX0">&nbsp;</span></span></p>
</div>
<div class="OutlineElement Ltr  BCX0 SCXO146644695">
<p class="Paragraph SCXO146644695 BCX0" lang="EN-US" xml:lang="EN-US"><span class="EOP SCXO146644695 BCX0" style="font-size: large;">&nbsp;</span></p>
</div>
<div class="OutlineElement Ltr  BCX0 SCXO146644695">
