<p class="Paragraph SCXO146644695 BCX0" lang="EN-US" xml:lang="EN-US"><span style="font-size: small;"><span class="EOP SCXO146644695 BCX0">&nbsp;</span></span></p>
<p class="Paragraph SCXO146644695 BCX0" lang="EN-US" xml:lang="EN-US"><span style="font-size: small;"><span class="EOP SCXO146644695 BCX0"><span class="TextRun SCXO146644695 BCX0" lang="EN-US" xml:lang="EN-US" data-contrast="auto">Each Facility Rental must go through an approval process to ensure our team is able to accommodate your event. Your deposit will be refunded within 48 hours if we cannot accommodate your booking request for any reason.</span></span></span></p>
