<p class="Paragraph SCXO146644695 BCX0" lang="EN-US" xml:lang="EN-US"><span style="font-size: small;"><span class="TextRun SCXO146644695 BCX0" lang="EN-US" xml:lang="EN-US" data-contrast="auto">The Facility Rental comes standard with access to the all escape rooms, free roam VR Arena, arcades &amp; lobby games; 12' table for catering/food, 2 party rooms and plenty of space in the lobby for seating.&nbsp;</span><span class="TextRun SCXO146644695 BCX0" lang="EN-US" xml:lang="EN-US" data-contrast="auto">Our escape games &amp; VR arena allow a max of 60 players in the same hour. Capacity is 200. Larger groups will be able to rotate among different experiences ensuring every guest is active during your event.</span><span class="EOP SCXO146644695 BCX0">&nbsp;</span></span></p>
</div>
