    [name] => Flee Escape and Zero Latency VR Summer Camp 2025 - Kids 9 and above
    [description] => <div style="max-width: 1100px; margin: auto; font-family: 'Segoe UI', sans-serif; color: #f4f4f4; background-color: #101820; padding: 40px 20px; border-radius: 16px; box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(0,255,255,0.1);">
<h1 style="text-align: center; font-size: 2.5em; color: #00fff7; margin-bottom: 10px;">�� Summer Camp 2025 at Flee Escape Rooms and Zero Latency VR</h1>
<p style="text-align: center; font-size: 1.2em; color: #d0d0d0; max-width: 800px; margin: auto;">Join the ultimate week of fun, puzzles, and immersive tech at <strong>Flee Escape Rooms</strong> &amp; <strong>Zero Latency VR Seattle</strong> in Redmond! Designed for kids aged <strong>10&ndash;16</strong>.</p>
<div style="display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; justify-content: center; gap: 40px; margin-top: 40px;">
<div style="flex: 1 1 300px;">
<h2 style="color: #00fff7;">�� What&rsquo;s Included</h2>
<ul style="line-height: 1.8; color: #e0e0e0; list-style: none; padding-left: 0;">
<li>✔ Daily Escape Room Adventures</li>
<li>✔ Free-Roaming VR Game Sessions</li>
<li>✔ Puzzle-Building Workshop</li>
<li>✔ Lunch &amp; Snacks Provided</li>
<li>✔ Safe &amp; Supervised Environment</li>
</ul>
</div>
<div style="flex: 1 1 300px;">
<h2 style="color: #00fff7;">�� Schedule</h2>
<ul style="line-height: 1.8; color: #e0e0e0; list-style: none; padding-left: 0;">
<li><strong>Time:</strong> 12:30 PM &ndash; 4:30 PM</li>
<li><strong>Days:</strong> Monday to Friday</li>
<li><strong>Starts:</strong> Weekly from June 17</li>
<li><strong>Location:</strong> Redmond, WA</li>
<li><strong>Age Group:</strong> 10 to 16 years</li>
</ul>
</div>
</div>
<div style="text-align: center; margin-top: 50px;">
<h2 style="color: #00fff7;">�� Reserve Your Spot Today!</h2>
<p style="color: #ccc; margin-bottom: 20px;">Limited seats. High demand. Register early for a week of epic memories!</p>
<p style="margin-top: 15px; font-size: 0.9em; color: #888;">Need help? Call us at (425) 287-1426 or email <a style="color: #00fff7;" href="mailto:info@fleeescape.com">info@fleeescape.com</a></p>
</div>
</div>
