                    [name] => 40% OFF VR GAME ADD ON - BUNDLE AND SAVE
                    [index] => 0
                    [description] => <div style="border: 2px solid #ff9800; border-radius: 8px; padding: 14px 16px; margin: 12px 0; background: #fff7e6; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 600px;">
<div style="font-size: 1.1rem; font-weight: bold; color: #e65100; margin-bottom: 6px;"><span style="font-size: large;">�� BUNDLE AND SAVE - Get Up to 40% Off <a title="Zero Latency VR Games" href="http://www.zerolatencyvr.com/en/seattle" target="_blank">Zero Latency VR</a>&nbsp;games!</span></div>
<div style="font-size: 0.95rem; color: #333; line-height: 1.4;">&nbsp;</div>
<div style="font-size: 0.95rem; color: #333; line-height: 1.4;"><span style="font-size: small;">Add an exhilarating 30 minute award-winning, Zero Latency VR game of your choice to your escape room booking and <strong>instantly save up to 40% OFF on your VR session</strong>. You can choose the VR game of your choice when you come in for your escape room session.</span></div>
<div style="font-size: 0.95rem; color: #333; line-height: 1.4;"><span style="font-size: small;">&nbsp;</span></div>
<div style="font-size: 0.95rem; color: #333; line-height: 1.4;">
