Array
(
    [name] => ESCAPE ROOM PARTY PACKAGE (Up to 16 players; 1 Hour Escape Rooms + 1 Hour Party in Lobby area)
    [description] => <p><strong><span class="TextRun SCXO146644695 BCX0" lang="EN-US" xml:lang="EN-US" data-contrast="auto">(Party Package booking must go through an approval process to ensure our team is able to accommodate your event. You can request the escape room of your choice that you would want to reserve as part of this package however we cannot guarantee those rooms will be available based on the time slot. If those escape rooms are not available, we will book the other ones that might be available)</span></strong></p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p>Host a very special day with FLEE Ultimate VR Arena and Escape Rooms!</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p>This is what our exciting Escape Room 2 Hour Party Package involves:</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<ol>
<li>1 Hour of Escape Rooms for 16 players. You will get 2 escape rooms of your choice (or whichever is available) with 8 players in each of the rooms.&nbsp;</li>
<li>Once the Escape Rooms are done, your group will get&nbsp;1 Hour of Party time in our open lobby area that includes a 14' party table with a decoration table cloth and 16 chairs. Note: If there is no prior party prior to your party package, we will give away the open lobby area for the entire duration of your event at no extra charge.</li>
</ol>
<p><br />You can bring any refreshments (cake, food, or drink), or decorations you require. If you need refrigeration for any of the items, we highly recommend upgrading to our private large party room instead that has a refrigerator, microwave, TV, Xbox, and a kitchenette and fits 35+ people. Large party room is $125/hr but available at a 50% discount as part of this package.</p>
